            </langmaterial>
    </did>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
            <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
                  <p>Includes minutes of Judiciary Board meetings; correspondence; newspaper clippings; material concerning student protest, 1970; records of the Student Conduct Committee, 1931-1968; Student Code, 1871-1959; and other records of the Men's Judiciary Board, the Undergraduate Judiciary Board, and the Freshman Judiciary Board at Cornell University.</p>
    </scopecontent>
